																		sudo rm -rf
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1841781&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610205836" alt="A Random Day" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1841781)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;" >A Random Day</a></span> <span class="odate time_1501598796 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">01 Aug 2017 14:46</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3562588">
									

<p>Part 2 of 3. Theme song is <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SchRMi0S_u8">Activation</a>, by <a href="https://lazerhawk.bandcamp.com/">Lazerhawk</a>.</p>
<p>This has been a long time coming, so it's bound to be much worse than T Minus. Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greenwolf" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1814684); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1814684&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1501598796" alt="GreenWolf" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1814684)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greenwolf" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1814684); return false;">GreenWolf</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1372582&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1501598796" alt="Jacob Conwell" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1372582)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;">Jacob Conwell</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aiden-eldritch" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2221240); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2221240&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1501598796" alt="Aiden Eldritch" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2221240)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aiden-eldritch" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2221240); return false;">Aiden Eldritch</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chaosera" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2227264); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2227264&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1501598796" alt="ChaoSera" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2227264)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chaosera" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2227264); return false;">ChaoSera</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2038009); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2038009&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1501598796" alt="TyGently" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2038009)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2038009); return false;">TyGently</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1229263); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1229263&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1501598796" alt="Roget" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1229263)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1229263); return false;">Roget</a></span>, and everyone else who looked at it.</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;On&nbsp;the&nbsp;next&nbsp;episode</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Stay&nbsp;tuned</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<blockquote>
<p>&quot;Demon-guided munitions in Korea, hunter-killer locusts in Vietnam, Mandelbrot vacuums in Afghanistan, basilisk grenades in the Gulf… the list goes on. But eigenweapons? The Americans and Soviets made a few more half-assed tries in the eighties and left us to contain their failures - it would be over thirty years before anyone figured out how to make eigenweapons not just practical, but profitable.&quot;</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
